SUPERSTORE SALES INSIGHTS - ANALYZING SALES DATA USING PYTHON¶

INTRODUCTION¶

Sales insights refer to the actionable information and understanding gained from analyzing sales data. It involves the process of examining sales data, patterns, trends, and metrics to extract valuable insights that can inform business decisions and strategies aimed at optimizing sales performance, increasing revenue, and enhancing customer satisfaction.

OBJECTIVES¶

The objectives of sales insights revolve around leveraging data-driven analysis to inform and optimize various aspects of the sales process, ultimately leading to increased revenue, improved customer satisfaction, and sustainable business growth.

Married women age group 26-35 yrs from UP, Maharastra and Karnataka working in IT, Healthcare and Aviation are more likely to buy products from Food and Clothing category.¶
